-- Draghi Ready to Explain Policies to Parliament: SZ
-- B y   J a m e s   K r a u s
-- 2012-09-14T05:18:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-14/draghi-ready-to-explain-policies-to-parliament-sz-correct-.html
(Corrects name of publication where
interview appears to Sueddeutsche Zeitung throughout.)
European Central Bank President  Mario Draghi  says he’s ready to
explain his policies to  Germany ’s parliament if invited,
Sueddeutsche Zeitung reports.
* Says “Will be good opportunity to explain what we’re doing,”
Sueddeutsche reports
* Polls showing almost half of Germans distrust the ECB
president make his work difficult, Draghi says: Sueddeutsche
* Says decision to approve unlimited purchases of bonds is most
criticized. Adds bonds will only be purchased if strict
conditions are met: Sueddeutsche
* Says “we have risks under control. Not to act would be more
risky,” Sueddeutsche reports
* Says reasons for the German opposition to his policies rooted
in Germany’s history and fear of inflation: Sueddeutsche  To contact the reporter on this story:
